source.name: Census 2000 Summary File 1 (SF1)
source.description: Basic information on the U.S. population from Census 2000. It includes data on people's age, sex, and race, their family and household groups, and whether their home is owned or rented. There are 286 Detailed Tables available in the SF 1 data product, many available for the nine major race groups. Data are published to the census block level or the census tract level.
